OL,6,FKatie Cole was at Newcastle Crown
OL,7,FCourt as Dr Thomas Kwan was sentenced
OL,8,Ffor attempted murder
OL,10,FA GP has been jailed for more than 30
OL,11,Fyears for trying to kill his mother's
OL,12,Fpartner with a fake Covid jab loaded
OL,13,Fwith poison while posing as a
OL,14,Fcommunity nurse.
OL,16,FDr Thomas Kwan was sentenced at
OL,17,FNewcastle Crown Court on Wednesday (6
OL,18,FNovember) having previously pleaded
OL,19,Fguilty to the attempted murder of
OL,20,FPatrick O'Hara.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/18
