OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F429A1731099696
OL,3,CGP who tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,FSentencing Kwan in a packed courtroom
OL,7,Fto 31 years and five months in prison,
OL,8,FMrs Justice Lambert condemned the
OL,9,F"callous and calculated" method which
OL,10,Fthe defendant adopted to gain entry
OL,11,Finto his victim's house.
OL,13,FShe said: "Your masquerade you struck
OL,14,Fat the heart of public confidence in
OL,15,Fthe healthcare profession."
OL,17,FVictim Patrick O'Hara says "justice
OL,18,Fhas been done" as reacts to the
OL,19,Fsentencing outside of court
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/18
