OL,3,CGP who tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,FThe court previously heard Kwan's
OL,7,Fmother, Jenny Leung, had been in a
OL,8,Frelationship with Mr O'Hara for 21
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FHer will stated that Mr O'Hara would
OL,12,Finherit a share of her home when she
OL,13,Fdied. But the married father-of-one,
OL,14,Fwho was "obsessed with money", did not
OL,15,Fapprove.
OL,17,FProsecutors said this struck at the
OL,18,Fvery heart of his sense of entitlement
OL,19,Fand led to him plotting to take Mr
OL,20,FO'Hara out of the picture.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/18
