OL,3,CGP who tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,FAt the start of November last year,
OL,7,FKwan sent his first fake NHS letter to
OL,8,FMr O'Hara, purporting to be from a
OL,9,Fcommunity nursing team, which advised
OL,10,Fhim he was eligible for a home visit
OL,11,Fand they would be in touch soon.
OL,13,FIn December, Kwan then cleared his
OL,14,Fdiary for the attack - booking a
OL,15,Fholiday for the end of January from
OL,16,Fhis work at Happy House Surgery, in
OL,17,FSunderland, where he was a GP and
OL,18,Fpartner.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/18
