OL,6,FHe checked in at the Premier Inn, in
OL,7,FNewgate Street, shortly before 2.45am
OL,8,Fwhere he had booked using a false name.
OL,10,FA few hours later he appeared on the
OL,11,Fhotel's cameras leaving his room,
OL,12,Fwearing a long coat, hat, mask and
OL,13,Fsurgical gloves.
OL,15,FThe GP was then tracked on CCTV making
OL,16,Fhis way on foot towards the city
OL,17,Fcentre home his mother and then
OL,18,Fpartner shared, on St Thomas Street.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/18
