OL,6,FMr O'Hara let the tinted-glasses-
OL,7,Fwearing 'community nurse' into the
OL,8,Fhouse where he spent 45 minutes.
OL,10,FAll the time speaking in what the
OL,11,Fcourt heard was broken English with an
OL,12,FAsian accent, Kwan carried out health
OL,13,Fchecks, a questionnaire, took bloods
OL,14,Fand his blood pressure.
OL,16,FThe doctor in disguise even took the
OL,17,Fblood pressure of his own mother
OL,18,Fbefore moving on to inject Mr O'Hara.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/18
