OL,6,FAs the needle of the supposed Covid
OL,7,Fbooster entered his arm, the victim
OL,8,Fdescribed flinching and feeling
OL,9,F"instant, excruciating pain" as Kwan
OL,10,Fhastily packed up his bag to leave.
OL,12,FThe court heard his mother, Ms Leung,
OL,13,Fmade a comment to Mr O'Hara that the
OL,14,Fnurse was the same height as her son -
OL,15,Fleading the victim to suspect
OL,16,Fsomething was seriously wrong.
OL,18,FTwo days later Mr O'Hara was taken
OL,19,Finto intensive care in hospital where,
OL,20,Fsuffering from a rare and flesh-eating
OL,21,Fdisease, he remained for weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/18
