OL,6,FWhen police were called to Mr O'Hara's
OL,7,Fbedside - he told them he was
OL,8,Fsuspicious that the nurse could have
OL,9,Fbeen Kwan.
OL,11,FTwo weeks after the attack, the GP was
OL,12,Farrested by police who found a haul of
OL,13,Fchemicals and associated equipment in
OL,14,Fhis detached garage.
OL,16,FAmong the array of chemicals was
OL,17,Farsenic and liquid mercury as well as
OL,18,Fcastor beans which can be used to make
OL,19,Fthe chemical weapon ricin.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/18
