OL,6,FPolice found a recipe for ricin on his
OL,7,Fcomputer but Ministry of Defence
OL,8,Fpoisons expert Professor Steven
OL,9,FEmmett, although still not sure which
OL,10,Fpoison was used, thought iodomethane
OL,11,Fwhich is commonly used in pesticides,
OL,12,Fwas more likely.
OL,14,FNewly released footage from
OL,15,FNorthumbria Police shows the moment
OL,16,Fdisgraced doctor Thomas Kwan was
OL,17,Farrested at his home
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/18
