OL,6,FA search of his home also revealed a
OL,7,Fmobile phone used to text Mr O'Hara
OL,8,Fand storage devices containing
OL,9,Fresearch materials on poisons,
OL,10,Fguidance on murder investigations, and
OL,11,Ftoxicology books including a book
OL,12,Fcalled '10 poisons used to kill
OL,13,Fpeople'.
OL,15,FKwan came before a jury charged with
OL,16,Fattempted murder but admitted his
OL,17,Fguilt on the second day of trial last
OL,18,Fmonth.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/18
