OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,FToday he was sentenced to 34 years
OL,7,Fimprisonment, reduced to 31 years and
OL,8,Ffive months on account of his guilty
OL,9,Fplea. He will serve two thirds of the
OL,10,Fsentence behind bars.
OL,12,FDuring sentencing, Mrs Justice Lambert
OL,13,Fsaid Kwan was not considered to be a
OL,14,Frisk to the wider public and therefore
OL,15,Fdid not hand him the life sentence the
OL,16,Fprosecution had called for.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/18
