OL,6,FMrs Justice Lambert told Kwan: "You
OL,7,Fset out to harm Mr O'Hara when he was
OL,8,Fin his own home, where he had every
OL,9,Fright to feel safe. You gained entry
OL,10,Fto his home in the most calculated and
OL,11,Fcallous of ways, under the guise of a
OL,12,Ftrusted healthcare professional.
OL,14,F"You sought and obtained his (and your
OL,15,Fmother's) trust by abusing your
OL,16,Fknowledge of the healthcare system by
OL,17,Ffaking letters purportedly from an NHS
OL,18,Finstitution.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/18
