OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F429A1731099696
OL,3,CGP who tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,F"They were good forgeries, but such is
OL,7,Fthe trust and confidence that Mr
OL,8,FO'Hara and your mother and the wider
OL,9,Fcommunity place in the NHS that no one
OL,10,Fwould have thought to review those
OL,11,Fletters in a critical way.
OL,13,F"I agree with the prosecution that the
OL,14,Fwider impact of your offending cannot
OL,15,Fbe ignored. By your masquerade you
OL,16,Fstruck at the heart of public
OL,17,Fconfidence in the healthcare
OL,18,Fprofession."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G15/18
