OL,3,CGP who tried to kill mother's partner
OL,4,Cwith poison jab jailed for 31 years
OL,6,FMrs Justice Lambert sentences Thomas
OL,7,FKwan to 31 years and five months
OL,8,Fbehind bars
OL,10,FPaul Greaney KC, defending Kwan,
OL,11,Fpreviously told the court there were
OL,12,F"mixed motives" behind the attempted
OL,13,Fmurder.
OL,15,FMr Greaney said: "This terrible scheme
OL,16,Fdid not have as its sole focus
OL,17,Ffinancial gain but was much more
OL,18,Fgenerally influenced by his feelings
OL,19,Fabout his relationship with his mother
OL,20,Fand the way she had treated him.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G16/18
